description:
Join the live stream of the 61st General Conference Session being held in St. Louis, Missouri, USA.

This morning following a digital music concert, Jongimpi Papu will present a worship message entitled, "What will You give me, and how will I inherit it?" Jongimpi Papu is currently serving as Ministerial and Family Ministries director for the Southern African-Indian Ocean Division. 

Following the worship, we will move directly into our morning business session. Nominating committee will continue to meet and bring back reports to the delegates throughout the day. You can access the session agenda here: https://www.gcsession.org/session-agenda/

Follow our church social media accounts to get more informational and inspirational posts throughout this week: 

ANN Website: https://adventist.news/ 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/adventistchurch/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/adventistchurch/ 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheAdventistChurch
